  "title": "SPA Store Manager",
  "description": "<p>SPA 店长:</p><p>工作职责（Job Responsibilities）</p><p>1. 负责美容 / SPA 门店的日常运营管理，确保门店顺畅运作</p><p>2. 管理并带领美容师团队，包括排班、培训及绩效跟进</p><p>3. 提升客户服务质量，处理客户咨询及客户关系维护</p><p>4. 负责门店销售目标管理，推动配套及产品销售</p><p>5.管理门店库存、耗材及成本控制</p><p>6. 配合总部完成相关行政及营运安排</p><p>7. 协助执行门店市场推广活动</p><p></p><p>任职要求（Job Requirements）</p><p>1.具备美容 / SPA 行业相关经验，有店长或管理经验者优先</p><p>2.熟悉门店日常运营流程</p><p>3.具备良好的沟通能力及团队管理能力</p><p>4.能以中文作为主要工作语言</p><p>5. 工作态度稳定，责任心强</p><p></p><p>三个员工：</p><p>1. 请说明你是否具备美容或 SPA 行业的相关工作经验？如有，请简要描述你的岗位及管理经验。</p><p>Do you have relevant working experience in the beauty or SPA industry? If yes, please briefly describe your role and any management experience.</p><p>2.你是否熟悉 SPA 门店的日常运营管理，包括人员管理、客户服务、销售目标及库存管理？</p><p>Are you familiar with the daily operations of a SPA outlet, including staff management, customer service, sales targets, and inventory management?</p><p>3. 你是否可以使用中文作为主要工作语言，与客户及团队进行日常沟通？</p><p>Are you able to use Mandarin Chinese as the main working language for daily communication with customers and team members?</p><p></p><p>Position: SPA Store Manager</p><p>Job Responsibilities</p><p>1.Oversee the daily operations of the beauty / SPA outlet to ensure smooth and efficient operations</p><p>2.Manage and lead the beautician team, including staff scheduling, training, and performance monitoring</p><p>3.Enhance customer service standards and handle customer enquiries and relationship management</p><p>4.Drive sales performance by managing sales targets and promoting service packages and products</p><p>5.Manage outlet inventory, consumables, and cost control</p><p>6.Coordinate with head office on administrative and operational matters</p><p>7.Assist in the execution of marketing and promotional activities for the outlet</p><p></p><p>Job Requirements</p><p>1. Relevant experience in the beauty / SPA industry; candidates with store manager or supervisory experience will be an advantage</p><p>2.Familiar with daily outlet operations and management processes</p><p>3.Strong communication and team management skills</p><p>4.Ability to use Mandarin Chinese as the main working language</p><p>5. Stable work attitude with a strong sense of responsibility</p>",
